ic)<br>- CL:<a href="/dictionary/塊">塊</a>|<a href="/dictionary/块">块</a>[kuai4]<br>- accented beat in Chinese music<br>- hard<br>- stiff<br>- to stop smiling or look serious<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">闆|板[<span style="color:#009900;">bǎn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- see <a href="/dictionary/老闆">老闆</a>|<a href="/dictionary/老板">老板</a>, boss<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">闆|板[<span style="color:#000099;">pàn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to catch sight of in a doorway (old)<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+677F</p></div>

